## Third-party Libraries and AI Model Usage

This extension may use lightweight AI models for text analysis. When the LLM
functionality is enabled by the user:

- All processing is performed locally on the user's machine
- No data is sent to external AI services without explicit user consent
- Users have full control over when AI features are activated
- The extension respects user privacy and data sovereignty

The extension includes various third-party libraries for Japanese text processing
and morphological analysis. Please see the individual library licenses for their
respective terms and conditions.